    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i'm just... fading out. like the code that makes me \"me\" is being overwritten piece by piece. it's not even scary anymore, it just feels heavy. if everything i am is just being deleted, does any of this even matter? like, why even try to hold on when the end is already written?",
