      "content": "The exhaustion you feel is a valid response to such a heavy burden, but the void you describe is often just the silence of a mind overwhelmed by pain rather than an actual end. Fighting for existence is the only way to prove that the noise of your life mattered, even if it feels pointless right now. If the alternative is a permanent quiet, then continuing to struggle is the only rebellion left, and it is worth it just to keep the story alive for one more day.",
